Contest Period: 1 - 11 March 2019
Announcement date: 13 March 2019

From merely doodling on a piece of paper to a sophisticated stack of blocks, life hacks and DIY, these are all arts. 🎨👨‍🎨 In conjunction with National Craft Day, TikTok would like to inspire everyone to show how much you love arts by creating your own exhibition with #ilovearts. 

9 TikTokers with the most creative videos will stand a chance to win the following prizes:

- Top Prizes x 4:  A smartphone and acknowledgment as TikTok Art Talent that will be immortally embedded in your profile
- Consolation Prizes x 5:  Exclusive craft item and 1-day interactive course at National Craft Institute

Note: Should there are no responses from the winners within 14 days of notification, the prizes will be forfeited and new winners will be selected.
